      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Var. b (mss. 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2109):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent" n="NerangTransc.a" xml:id="Y8.3NerangTransc.a" xml:lang="Pahl"><em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē bār guftan dast az barsom ul hištan sar ī zōhr nihuftan srōšdrōn xwardan ud dahān pāk kardan ud dast pad pādyāb kardan dast abar barsom nihādan <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> čahār guftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent" n="NerangEnglish.a" xml:id="Y8.3NerangEnglish.a">"He should say three Aṣ̌əm Vohū. He should release his hand from the barsom and cover the top of the zōhr. He should eat the <em>srōšdrōn</em>, clean his mouth and wash his hand with padyāb and lay his hand on the barsom.</ab>
      </Nerangs>
